Someday there will be
a gay president.

265
00:17:59,344 --> 00:18:02,370
Maybe there'll even be
a gay, black president.

266
00:18:02,448 --> 00:18:06,145
But one combination
I do not see happening
is gay, black and dead.

267
00:18:07,886 --> 00:18:09,945
