334
00:22:49,901 --> 00:22:52,665
Well, I guess you can't
be around that much niceness
and not get any on you.

335
00:22:52,738 --> 00:22:55,070
Is that why you haven't put
the moves on her?

336
00:22:55,140 --> 00:22:58,735
